-- California Same-Sex Marriage Ban Denies `Fundamental Right,' Judge Is Told
-- Karen Gullo
-- 2010-06-16T17:18:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/california-same-sex-marriage-ban-denies-fundamental-right-judge-is-told.html

          
          
             A lawyer for gay couples urged a
federal judge to overturn California’s ban on same-sex marriage,
saying at the close of a trial that moral disapproval doesn’t
justify denying the “fundamental right” to wed.  
